{"title":"Stinner Frameworks Launches Refugio Select Gravel Bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/stinner-frameworks-launches-refugio-select-gravel-bike/","date":1736866361000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Stinner Frameworks Refugio Select outdoors\" /></p>\n<p>he If you’re familiar with the Stinner Frameworks, you know they offer a few different series options. You can choose between; Custom (fully custom design), Podium (titanium), and Select (premium US-Made steel). The Refugio adventure machine is now available to the masses in the Stinner Select Series and starts at $1,695 vs. $3,599 for the Custom Series model (for the frameset only).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-just-bike-rider--jpg.webp\"><img width=\"7935\" height=\"5076\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-just-bike-rider--jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-just-bike-rider--jpg.webp 7935w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-just-bike-rider--297x190.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-just-bike-rider--1536x983.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-just-bike-rider--120x77.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-just-bike-rider--768x491.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>All Photos: Stinner Frameworks</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>What is the Stinner Refugio?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The rugged climbs and winding roads of Refugio Road in Santa Barbara, CA (where Stinner calls home) inspired the Refugio name. From steep ascents to gnarly descents, this bike is ready to tackle the toughest routes confidently – plus, it looks fantastic in Lake or Trailhead colorways.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-badge--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1278\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-badge--1536x1278.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-badge--1536x1278.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-badge--297x247.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-badge--120x100.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-badge--768x639.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-badge--2048x1704.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-logo-blue--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-logo-blue--1536x1024.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-logo-blue--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-logo-blue--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-logo-blue--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-logo-blue--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-logo-blue--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-logo-blue--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-logo-blue--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>What Does Select Series Mean? </h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Refugio Select is handcrafted from a blend of Columbus Zona and Life steel tubing as part of the Stinner Select Series. Each frame is fabricated, painted, and assembled in Santa Barbara, CA, underscoring Stinner’s commitment to US-made craftsmanship. The main difference here is that this is an off-the-shelf geometry for Stinner, instead of the custom geometry and options found on the aptly named Custom Series. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-rider--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"2058\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-rider--scaled.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-rider--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-rider--297x239.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-rider--1536x1235.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-rider--120x96.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-rider--768x617.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-rider--2048x1647.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Steel Adventure</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Refugio Select features clearance for 50mm tires, making it an ideal choice for gravel grinders, bikepackers, and endurance cyclists. The bike is built with UDH compatibility and thoughtfully designed mounts for fenders, triple fork legs, and dynamo lights, ensuring it’s ready for multi-day adventures or spirited local rides.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Stinner Refugio Select Geometry</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Refugio-Select-Geometery-.png\"><img width=\"1690\" height=\"954\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Refugio-Select-Geometery-.png\" alt=\"Refugio Select Geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Refugio-Select-Geometery-.png 1690w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Refugio-Select-Geometery--297x168.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Refugio-Select-Geometery--1536x867.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Refugio-Select-Geometery--120x68.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Refugio-Select-Geometery--768x434.png 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>“The Refugio Select is the ultimate adventure machine. It’s designed to handle the most challenging routes with reliability and style, giving riders the confidence to explore without limits.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Aaron Stinner, founder of Stinner Frameworks</em></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--jpg.webp\"><img width=\"7933\" height=\"5291\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--jpg.webp 7933w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-outdoors--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Performance Meets Accessibility</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Select Series combines high-quality materials and craftsmanship with an accessible price point, offering riders a “forever bike” that doesn’t break the bank. The Refugio Select is available in six stock sizes and is equipped with SRAM AXS 12-speed drivetrain, DT Swiss wheels, and an Easton cockpit.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-select--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-select--1536x1024.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-select--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-select--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-select--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-select--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-select--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-select--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-select--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-name--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-name--1536x1024.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-name--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-name--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-name--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-name--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-name--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-name--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-name--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-gravel--jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1025\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-gravel--1536x1025.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-gravel--1536x1025.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-gravel--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-gravel--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-gravel--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-gravel--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select-gravel--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Key Features:</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Comfortable, all-day geometry</li>\n\n\n\n<li>700x50c tire clearance</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Stinner-designed UDH dropouts (160mm flat mount)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Durable powder coat finish (colors: <em>Trailhead</em> and <em>Lake</em>)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"973\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select--1536x973.webp\" alt=\"Stinner Frameworks Refugio Select\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select--1536x973.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select--297x188.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select--120x76.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select--768x487.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Frameworks-Refugio-Select--2048x1298.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Specifications at a Glance:</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Frame Material:</strong> Columbus Zona/Life steel tubing</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Drivetrain:</strong> SRAM Apex/GX Eagle Transmission AXS</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Mounts:</strong> Fender, triple fork leg, front light, and internal dynamo routing</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>MSRP:</strong> $3,995 (complete build) / $1,695 (frameset)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>For more details, visit<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://stinnerframeworks.com/\"> Stinner Frameworks</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/stinner-frameworks-launches-refugio-select-gravel-bike/\">Stinner Frameworks Launches Refugio Select Gravel Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"8153d5964b4930d94cf2b9bfae2587cbe70dec0acc804738267c0ddf6f04248d","category":"Cycling"}